♪ Bayangan terus bergoyang ♪

00:19:35.850 --> 00:19:38.600
♪ Burung phoenix melawan cahaya ♪

00:19:39.120 --> 00:19:41.940
♪ Telah mencari sejauh seribu mil ♪

00:19:42.300 --> 00:19:45.480
♪ Seiring berlalunya waktu, debu beterbangan,
